Module HW08
Package provided.datapacket

Interface IDataPacketID

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DataPacketIDFactory.DataPacketID
public interface IDataPacketID
extends java.io.Serializable
A host ID value compatible with ADataPackets The implementation of this interface is immaterial. It only has to follow the Java rules for object equality, i.e. the rules governing the behavior of the hashCode() and equals() methods. This enables two completely different ID value implementations to be used to represent the same data type, so long as they are "equal".
Author:
